{"tid":1952022,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"覺唔覺TVB係咁比張宇人上鏡？","createTime":"2020-03-31T10:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T10:46:42.000Z","uid":198258,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"21a22c6b230d587387f2d8cec617bbab8683a8be","tid":1952022,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"我知大家冇睇TVB，所以幫大家會報下。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭講禁酒之後張宇人就出黎講下反對呀，要政府資助呀。得個講字但係TVB就係咁播，搞到好似佢施壓緊政府，但明明佢一直都係林鄭忠實嘅擦鞋狗。<br />\n<br />\n懷疑禁酒令除左林鄭忽撚左之外，有可以係順便做場假割蓆幫下張宇人呢條擦鞋狗。依家天下人都知道林鄭已經係黃藍皆棄，要保民望就要及早遠離佢。<br />\n<br />\n請大家大力推廣呢條討張宇人檄文片，<br />\n由其係推比食店老闆，特別係淺藍中立。或者直情係餐廳到大大聲播出黎。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/nN_AkoGziAo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FnN_AkoGziAo&d=J1zZABjvT6n5gtW5jiJIhpUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=278fe8eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/nN_AkoGziAo</a>"},{"pid":"c33a445044acc15d9f5e6b1c7257743cbb491697","tid":1952022,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:44:38.000Z","msg":"Thx"},{"pid":"cc4fb26b2b5d6a2316048da53a93ac9a1f7a4750","tid":1952022,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:45:06.000Z","msg":"sorry 無人睇cctvb"},{"pid":"aa771825dae1be609bf587ea9d54ec84222fd440","tid":1952022,"uid":198258,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cc4fb26b2b5d6a2316048da53a93ac9a1f7a4750","tid":1952022,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:45:06.000Z","msg":"sorry 無人睇cctvb"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T10:46:42.000Z","msg":"咁了解下港豬接收緊咩資訊都要嘅"}]}